```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Flask Server
    participant H as Human Captcha
    participant Bot as Bot Simulation
    participant A as Analytics
    
    U->>B: Request /api/captcha
    B->>S: GET /api/captcha
    S->>H: Generate Maze
    H->>S: Return Human Captcha Data
    S->>B: JSON Response with Maze Image
    
    U->>B: Draw Human Path
    B->>S: POST /api/verify
    S->>H: Validate Path
    H->>S: Return Verification Result
    
    U->>B: Simulate Bot
    B->>S: POST /api/bot-simulate
    S->>Bot: Call create_bot()
    Bot->>S: Return Bot Path Data
    S->>Bot: Validate Path
    Bot->>S: Analyze Behavior
    S->>A: Update Analytics
    S->>B: Return Bot Detection Result
    
    B->>S: GET /api/analytics
    S->>B: Return Real-time Stats
    
    Note over S,B: Decoupled Bot Simulation<br/>Human vs Bot Captchas Side-by-Side
```